---
---
<section id="projects" class="section projects-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="badge badge-green">Production Registry</span>
      <h2 class="section-title-center">Active utilities built for the student body</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle-center">
        Each project addresses a specific hurdle in campus life. Every repository is audited for data leaks and operates completely client-side.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <!-- Project: Room TBA -->
      <div class="card project-card">
        <div class="project-preview">
          <div class="preview-header">
            <span class="preview-url">room-tba.uplbtools.me</span>
          </div>
          <img src="/room-tba-screenshot.png" alt="Room TBA screenshot preview" class="preview-img" />
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-meta">
          <div class="meta-tags">
            <span class="tag tag-maroon">Interactive Map</span>
            <span class="tag">NextJS</span>
            <span class="tag">Open Source</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Room TBA</h3>
          <p>
            An interactive 3D map interface designed to help UPLB students look up empty rooms, review schedules by building, and find routes. Reduces registration friction by giving students immediate visual access to academic schedules.
          </p>
          <div class="meta-actions">
            <a href="https://room-tba.uplbtools.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">
              <span>Launch Utility</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/uplbtools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary">
              <span>Repository</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Project: GradeSim -->
      <div class="card project-card">
        <div class="project-preview">
          <div class="preview-header">
            <span class="preview-url">gradesim.uplbtools.me</span>
          </div>
          <img src="/gradesim-screenshot.png" alt="GradeSim screenshot preview" class="preview-img" />
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-meta">
          <div class="meta-tags">
            <span class="tag tag-green">Browser Extension</span>
            <span class="tag">GWA Tools</span>
            <span class="tag">Local storage</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Elbi GradeSim</h3>
          <p>
            A lightweight extension compatible with Chrome, Firefox, and Edge. Integrates directly with the UPLB AMIS portal interface, automating GWA calculations and simulating the remaining units needed to meet academic honors criteria.
          </p>
          <div class="meta-actions">
            <a href="https://gradesim.uplbtools.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-green">
              <span>Get Extension</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/uplbtools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary">
              <span>Repository</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Future Tool Teaser (Clean, solid, no glowing effects) -->
    <div class="card teaser-card">
      <div class="teaser-content">
        <h3>Have a tool idea to optimize campus enlistment or navigation?</h3>
        <p>We are a growing community looking to collaborate. If you are developing a local utility, or have a product wireframe that solves a student issue, we can help you review, host, and maintain it under the organization.</p>
        <a href="#community" class="btn btn-secondary">
          <span>Pitch a Project</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects-section {
    background-color: #090b11;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .section-title-center {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .section-subtitle-center {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .project-card {
    padding: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .project-preview {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background-color: #0c0d14;
  }
  
  .preview-header {
    height: 32px;
    background-color: #0d0e14;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  
  .preview-url {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }
  
  .preview-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.95;
    transition: var(--transition-fast);
  }
  
  .project-card:hover .preview-img {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  
  .project-meta {
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  
  .meta-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    background-color: #171923;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--text-body);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  
  .tag-maroon {
    color: #ef4444;
    border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
  }
  
  .tag-green {
    color: #10b981;
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  }
  
  .project-meta h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .project-meta p {
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-body);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  
  .meta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .teaser-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-color: var(--border-subtle);
  }
  
  .teaser-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .teaser-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .projects-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
